{"tid":1463391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放燃燒彈燒傷警察，應唔應該自首？","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:12:16.000Z","uid":283968,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2185ed8a4e24a9eed1b61345c0ca647d3ee5f189","tid":1463391,"uid":283968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警！快啲自首啦！燒傷同事啦！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑警用埋啲陰濕招數，扮示威者、匿私家車、近距離開槍、室內催淚彈、暴力拘捕、濫捕，最重要係！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">還眼！還眼！還眼！</span></span><br />\n黑警仲話傷者隻眼非由布袋彈所致，室內既煙係示威者施放滅火筒，臥底滲入示威者係無問題，你當香港市民傻嫁！？的確，有班長輩就係人講乜就信乜，<span style=\"color: red;\">TVB既報導離晒大譜，誤導觀眾。</span><br />\n所以守護香城Youtube頻道既製作組日夜趕工，製作咗幾條以811事件為主題既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">長輩片</span></strong>，勞煩在座各位可以幫家中長輩訂閱頻道，睇片留言將影片成為推薦影片，盡可能集合大家既能力將影片成為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Youtube熱門</ins></strong></span>，觸及更多觀眾！<br />\n最後，頻道上月所賺得既營利：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1060港元</span></span></strong>(雖然唔多)，將會全數捐俾<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爆眼既女傷者</span></span></strong>(等待捐款途經)。希望大家繼續支持我地，所有影片都有意義，分享俾更多人睇！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">［811事件 - 狗扮人］</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fJcHc9YumyU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfJcHc9YumyU&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=3034ce7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fJcHc9YumyU</a><br />\n<br />\n頻道連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Ffreehongkong&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=84cd7159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong</a><br />\n<br />\n頻道計劃：<br />\n經過巴打絲打既意見，暫時決定會影印啲宣傳單張貼係連儂牆。有巴打提議過，不如學港人港地整youtube廣告，但當中涉及金錢，同需要製作廣告影片，所以依個計劃會再作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;【回顧】&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n為藍絲長輩而設既Youtube頻道正式面世！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1431722/page/22?post=535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1431722/page/22?post=535</a>"},{"pid":"8b2799e894b0b791c16a8a737ca2391fad5d1fd5","tid":1463391,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"a1e1676c8f4f382121eefd861e7dabef54e636c9","tid":1463391,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"308a12dc4977783aeeb4d3c2a87c36a4c7d28db9","tid":1463391,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:57:38.000Z","msg":"唔好搞住互屌"},{"pid":"088e55c8baaa12d7a9799e265aac75a865b91d90","tid":1463391,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"文宣一樣重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2343cea041bdc2bb8948895999c2c7f309d1ed1","tid":1463391,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75890898cfe9d0e75129dc1ce6d57dbd85a980de","tid":1463391,"uid":305185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"收皮啦！燒傷個張相只係紅左兩個膝頭，話唔定其實係仆街嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992c6de01dd2ac645ccc892e0b041a45cdbc33a7","tid":1463391,"uid"